     `tcl_output ([<list_1>, ..., <list_n>], <i>)' prints the <i>'th
     elements of <list_1>, ..., <list_n>.

     Examples:

          (%i1) tcl_output ([1, 2, 3, 4, 5, 6], 1, 3)$

           {1.000000000     4.000000000
           }
          (%i2) tcl_output ([1, 2, 3, 4, 5, 6], 2, 3)$

           {2.000000000     5.000000000
