          (%i4) tcl_output ([x1, y1, x2, y2, x3, y3], 2)$

           {$Y1 $Y2 $Y3
           }
          (%i5) tcl_output ([[1, 2, 3], [11, 22, 33]], 1)$

           {SIMP 1.000000000     11.00000000
