     Weibull(2,1/b), therefore when Maxima has not enough information
     to get the result, a noun form based on the Weibull density is
     returned.

          (%i1) load (distrib)$
          (%i2) pdf_rayleigh(x,b);
                                                  1
          (%o2)                 pdf_weibull(x, 2, -)
                                                  b
          (%i3) assume(x>0,b>0)$ pdf_rayleigh(x,b);
                                              2  2
                                     2     - b  x
          (%o4)                   2 b  x %e


